---
title: Quick Indian Coconut Chicken Curry & Garlic Rice with Tomato Salad & Coriander
description: This easy unforgettable Indian chicken curry gets the royal treatment with simmered spices, aromatic garlic rice and a finish of
creamy coconut sauce. Who knew something that takes so little effort could be so tasty?

*This recipe is under 550kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*

*We’ve replaced the radish in this recipe with tomato due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
